ABUJA – The Sokoto Rima River Basin Development Authority (SRRBDA) has commended President Muhammadu Buhari for being a leader who recognizes and rewards honesty, hard work, and dedication in service to humanity. The Authority stated this in Abuja when its Board members led by the Managing Director, Engr. Buhari Muhammed paid a congratulatory visit to the Chairman of the Board, Dr Ramatu Tijjani Aliyu in her office. Speaking on behalf of the Board, Hon. Godwin Bazari, commended President Muhammadu Buhari over the appointment of the Board chairman, as FCT Minister of State and lauded the enormous contributions of Dr Ramatu Tijjani Aliyu. Mr Austine Elemue, the media aid to the minister in a press statement made available to newsmen in Abuja said, “We are here on behalf of Sokoto Rima River Basin Development Authority to celebrate you for your tenacity and to commend President Muhammadu Buhari for your well-deserved appointment as Minister of State for FCT.